147
00:10:54,180 --> 00:10:58,580
Saksi, lalu kenapa awalnya
kau bilang tak berada di TKP?

148
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:00,820
Seseorang meninggal di sana.

149
00:11:01,380 --> 00:11:03,720
